title: Royal family ‘superfan’ prepares for upcoming wedding
text:
Royal family ‘superfan’ prepares for upcoming wedding 7:50am EDT - 01:38 
Donna Werner, a self-proclaimed 'superfan' of the British royal family, plans on flying across the sea and camping out on the street for the wedding of Prince Harry and American actress Meghan Markle's wedding.
